                        "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"
                    },
                    "body": "Excellent. \u00a0[https://arrow.apache.org/docs/python/generated/pyarrow.parquet.write_table.html] correctly documents the uint32 limitation.\u00a0 I did not anticipate the limitation when reading\u00a0 [https://arrow.apache.org/docs/python/api/datatypes.html.|https://arrow.apache.org/docs/python/api/datatypes.html] \u00a0For me, this is resolved.",
